UTzozo uveze ukuthi yena ungomunye wabantu besilisa abathanda ukuba sothandweni namantombazane amancane. Ubekhuluma ngaphansi kwesihloko esithi Blessers, lapho bekulindeleke ukuthi kufike usaziwayo wakuleli uKhanyi Mbau, ogcine engafikanga. "Ngiyiphilile impilo lapho ngilala khona nabesifazane abaningi ngobusuku obubodwa..." Udaba oluphelele kwiSolezwe lanamhlanje ekhasini lesibili.